# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Sode no Shirayuki — environment configuration
# Copy to `.env.local` for local dev. For Vercel, set these in:
#   Project Settings → Environment Variables
# Only ONE variable is required: API_BASE_URL. Everything else has a default.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Upstream scraper. The default (`shirayuki-scrapper-api-v2.vercel.app`) is the
# project's own hosted scraper. Override only if you're running a self-hosted
# scraper (see `lib/providers/*/client.ts` for all callers).
API_BASE_URL=https://shirayuki-scrapper-api-v2.vercel.app

# Set by Vercel automatically — don't override unless you know why.
# NODE_ENV=production
